<li id="cite_note-87"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-87">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFAgrawalTaguchiRamalingam2011">Agrawal, Taguchi &amp; Ramalingam 2011</a>.</span>
