<li id="cite_note-121"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-121">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFSabra1978b">Sabra 1978b</a>, p.&#160;121, n. 13</span>
