<li id="cite_note-168"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-168">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFRashed2007">Rashed 2007</a>, pp.&#160;8–9; <a href="#CITEREFTopdemir2007">Topdemir 2007</a></span>
