<li id="cite_note-onTheLightOfTheStars-169"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-onTheLightOfTheStars_169-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Ibn Al-Haytham, W. 'Arafat and H. J. J. Winter (1971) <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/4025317">(c.1027-1038)  The Light of the Stars: A Short Discourse by Ibn Al-Haytham </a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220921160132/https://www.jstor.org/stable/4025317">Archived</a> 21 September 2022 at the <a href="/wiki/Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine">Wayback Machine</a> <i>The British Journal for the History of Science</i> Vol. <b>5</b>, No. 3 (Jun., 1971), pp. 282-288 (7 pages) via JSTOR</span>
</li>
